      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for someone looking for dependable transportation. The engine starts up consistently and it is currently in good running order, though it shows some signs of its age with minor cosmetic wear and tear on the interior and exterior. It has been maintained regularly, but a new owner should expect to perform some standard upkeep soon. Overall, it's a solid, functional car that gets the job done without any major mechanical issues.",
