    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "$36,500 - Get ready for a fantastic ride with this well-maintained beauty! This car is in good condition and has clearly been cared for, offering a smooth driving experience and a clean look. While it shows some light, expected signs of use, it remains a reliable and stylish choice for anyone seeking a quality vehicle. Come see why this dependable car is the perfect fit for your daily commute or weekend getaways!",
